9027080#t19027080","upictitle":"GeekFurious: pic#121411156","article":"Congratulations, everyone involved.<br /><br />Granted, I have a hard time taking these awards seriously when they nominate the WORST \"Doctor Who\" season for that many awards. Granted, they hit the 50th anniversary special out of the park. <br /><br />\"Rains\" was superior to all nominated. But if it loses to \"Day\", then at least I can kind of understand. If it loses to anything else, I promise to set fire to my Hugo when I accept it in 2017.<br /><br />That's a guarantee. You can hold me to that or I'm not Geek of the house Furious.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 years ago","ctime":"April 20 2014, 18:45:56 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Well earned","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/GeekFurious","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"GeekFurious","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_2058420","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=65344279&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"GeekFurious","ctime_ts":1398019556,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/108712693/35465212","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/367496.html?replyto=19027336","name":"reply","title":"Reply","footer":1},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/367496.html?thread=19027336#t19027336","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/367496.html?thread=19027336#t19027336","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/367496.html?thread=19027336#t19027336","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_446304","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://www.facebook.com/jeremy.scholem","statpre